# Cross-origin isolation headers (Netlify / Cloudflare Pages format).
# Optional: the app works without them (the grid is transferred to the main
# thread via postMessage, not SharedArrayBuffer). They enable cross-origin
# isolation so `SharedArrayBuffer` — and a future wasm-threads build — become
# available. Vite copies files in `public/` to the site root at build time.
/*
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: require-corp
